{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I was asked by Wilsonart International,"},{"time":4000,"text":"a plastic laminate company, which is"},{"time":7000,"text":"the largest plastic laminate company in the world --"},{"time":9000,"text":"they asked me to design"},{"time":13000,"text":"a trade show booth"},{"time":15000,"text":"for exhibition at the International Contemporary Furniture Fair"},{"time":19000,"text":"in New York, in 2000."}]},{"cues":[{"time":21000,"text":"So looking at their three main markets"},{"time":25000,"text":"for their product which were basically"},{"time":28000,"text":"transportation design,"},{"time":31000,"text":"interiors and furniture,"},{"time":34000,"text":"we came up with the solution of taking"},{"time":36000,"text":"an old Airstream trailer and gutting it,"},{"time":39000,"text":"and trying to portray laminate,"},{"time":42000,"text":"and a trailer, in kind of a"},{"time":44000,"text":"fresh, new contemporary look."},{"time":46000,"text":"When this trailer showed up at my shop"},{"time":49000,"text":"in Berkeley, I'd actually never stepped foot in"},{"time":51000,"text":"an Airstream trailer, or any other trailer."},{"time":54000,"text":"So I can be somebody that can look at this"},{"time":56000,"text":"in a totally fresh perspective and see if I can"},{"time":59000,"text":"optimize it in its most idealistic fashion."},{"time":62000,"text":"I decided I had to do some research"},{"time":65000,"text":"and really figure out what had gone wrong"},{"time":67000,"text":"somewhere along the history of Airstream."},{"time":70000,"text":"What I discovered in these interiors is that"},{"time":73000,"text":"there was a disconnect between the exterior shell"},{"time":76000,"text":"and the interior architecture of the pieces."},{"time":78000,"text":"In that the shell was originally conceived"},{"time":82000,"text":"as a lightweight, modern, futuristic,"},{"time":86000,"text":"high-tech pod for hurtling down the freeway, and"},{"time":90000,"text":"the interiors were completely out of sync with that."},{"time":93000,"text":"In fact it appeared like they"},{"time":96000,"text":"referenced a mountain cabin."}]},{"cues":[{"time":99000,"text":"That seemed really like a crisis to me,"},{"time":101000,"text":"that they had never been able to"},{"time":103000,"text":"develop a vocabulary"},{"time":105000,"text":"about escape, and about travel, and modernity"},{"time":109000,"text":"in this trailer that was consistent with the shell."},{"time":111000,"text":"We really needed to do some archeology"},{"time":115000,"text":"in the trailer itself to figure out what's authentic"},{"time":117000,"text":"in an Airstream trailer,"},{"time":119000,"text":"and what feels like it has true purpose and utility."},{"time":122000,"text":"We stripped out all the vinyl"},{"time":124000,"text":"and zolatone paint that was covering up"},{"time":126000,"text":"this just fantastic aluminum shell."},{"time":129000,"text":"We took off all the visible hardware and trim"},{"time":132000,"text":"that was kind of doing the country cabin thing."},{"time":135000,"text":"I literally drew on the walls of the trailer,"},{"time":139000,"text":"mocked it up in cardboard,"},{"time":141000,"text":"we'd come in and cut, decide things were wrong,"},{"time":144000,"text":"pull it out, put it back in."}]},{"cues":[{"time":146000,"text":"The main goal was to smooth out the interior,"},{"time":150000,"text":"and begin to speak about motion,"},{"time":153000,"text":"and mobility, and independence."},{"time":156000,"text":"The biggest difficulty on one of these trailers"},{"time":159000,"text":"is that when you're designing there's actually no"},{"time":162000,"text":"logical place to stop and start materials"},{"time":166000,"text":"because of the continuous form of the trailer."},{"time":168000,"text":"There's no such things as two walls and a ceiling"},{"time":171000,"text":"coming together, where you can change materials and shapes."},{"time":174000,"text":"So that became a challenge."},{"time":176000,"text":"Compounding that,"},{"time":178000,"text":"the material of choice, laminate,"},{"time":180000,"text":"that I was trying to highlight,"},{"time":182000,"text":"only bends in two dimensions."},{"time":184000,"text":"It's a compound curve interior."},{"time":186000,"text":"What I had to devise was"},{"time":188000,"text":"a way of fooling the eye"},{"time":192000,"text":"into believing that all these panels"},{"time":195000,"text":"are curved with the shell."}]},{"cues":[{"time":197000,"text":"What I came up with was"},{"time":199000,"text":"a series of second skins"},{"time":201000,"text":"that basically float over the aluminum shell."},{"time":206000,"text":"And what I was trying to do there was"},{"time":208000,"text":"direct your eye in the space,"},{"time":210000,"text":"so that you would perceive the geometry in a different way,"},{"time":213000,"text":"and that the casework wouldn't break up the space."},{"time":218000,"text":"They also gave us a way to run power"},{"time":220000,"text":"and rewire the trailer without tearing out the skin,"},{"time":222000,"text":"so they function as an electrical chase."},{"time":225000,"text":"That's the trailer, pretty much finished."}]},{"cues":[{"time":227000,"text":"That trailer led to another commission,"},{"time":230000,"text":"to participate in whats called Tokyo Designers Block."},{"time":234000,"text":"Its a week of furniture design events in Tokyo, in October."},{"time":238000,"text":"Teruo Kurosaki, who owns a furniture company called Idee,"},{"time":241000,"text":"he asked me to ship him two trailers to Tokyo."},{"time":245000,"text":"He said one he would like to"},{"time":248000,"text":"make a real trailer, functioning, and we would sell that one."},{"time":252000,"text":"Trailer number two, you have a blank slate, you can to anything you want."}]},{"cues":[{"time":255000,"text":"We came up with a fantasy scenario"},{"time":257000,"text":"of a DJ traveling around the States,"},{"time":259000,"text":"that would collect records and go on tours."},{"time":262000,"text":"This trailer housed two turntables,"},{"time":265000,"text":"mixer, wet bar, fridge, integrated sound system."},{"time":269000,"text":"It's got a huge couch, fits quite a few people,"},{"time":272000,"text":"and basically we'd had a great time with this."},{"time":275000,"text":"And so in this trailer I took it upon myself to think about travel,"},{"time":278000,"text":"and escape, in an idiosyncratic sense."},{"time":282000,"text":"A lot of these ideas migrated into"},{"time":284000,"text":"the production trailers for Airstream."}]},{"cues":[{"time":287000,"text":"This brings us up to the time that I started consulting to Airstream."},{"time":291000,"text":"They came to me and said,"},{"time":293000,"text":"\"Well, what can we do to freshen this thing up?"},{"time":295000,"text":"And do you think kids, you know, skateboarders, surfers,"},{"time":299000,"text":"rock climbers, would use these things?\""},{"time":301000,"text":"And I said, \"Well, not in that interior.\""},{"time":304000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":305000,"text":"Anyway, I went out to Airstream"},{"time":307000,"text":"about six times during the process of building this prototype,"},{"time":310000,"text":"and it's called the Bambi prototype."},{"time":312000,"text":"I thought, \"Finally, oh yeah great,"},{"time":314000,"text":"big company, I'm gonna work with somebody with money"},{"time":316000,"text":"for tooling and molding.\""},{"time":319000,"text":"And I walked in their prototype facility, and"},{"time":322000,"text":"it's exactly like my shop, only bigger --"},{"time":325000,"text":"same tools, same things."},{"time":327000,"text":"So the problem became -- and they set this dilemma to me --"},{"time":331000,"text":"that you have to design the interior using only our existing technology,"},{"time":336000,"text":"and there's no money for tooling or molding."},{"time":338000,"text":"The trailers themselves are actually hand-built."},{"time":341000,"text":"All the casework is hand-scribed in, uniquely,"},{"time":344000,"text":"so you can't just cut 100 parts for 100 trailers,"},{"time":348000,"text":"you have to cut them big, and every single one is hand-fit."},{"time":351000,"text":"They didn't want to go to a componentized system."},{"time":355000,"text":"And there it is, that's the Bambi 16."},{"time":359000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}